I '''Alvin Toffler''' (mibait October 4, 1928) metung yang Americanung talasulat ampong [[futurist]], a pikabaluan kareng kayang obrang dikil king [[digital revolution]], [[Telecommunication|rebolusyon king komunikasyun]] ampong [[technological singularity]].

I Toffler sadya yang kadwang talapatuntun (''former associate editor'') ning magasin a ''[[Fortune (magasin)|Fortune]]''. Kareng mumuna nang obra, makatutuk ya king teknolohiya ampo reng kayang epektu antimo ing [[information overload]]. Minalis ya king pamanyuri king reaksyon kareng [[Social change|pamagbayu king ketawan o sosiedad]] (''changes in society''). Ing mas tauli nang obra, tungkul king daragul a upaya da reng kasangkapang militar ning ka-21ng dilanwa (''increasing power of 21st-century military hardware''), ing pamikalat da reng bayung teknolohiya, ampo ing kapitalismu.

